				<description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;hi-there-im-铅秋-&#34;&gt;Hi there, I&amp;rsquo;m 铅秋 👋&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I am currently a Master&amp;rsquo;s student at &lt;strong&gt;Peking University&lt;/strong&gt; (Class of 2025), and I obtained my undergraduate degree from &lt;strong&gt;Sichuan University&lt;/strong&gt; (Class of 2021).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My research interests include &lt;strong&gt;VLM&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;RLHF&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;MLsys&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-im-working-on&#34;&gt;What I&amp;rsquo;m Working On&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🤖 &lt;strong&gt;VLM / RLHF&lt;/strong&gt;: Vision-language models and reinforcement learning from human feedback (training, alignment, evaluation).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;⚙️ &lt;strong&gt;MLsys&lt;/strong&gt;: Machine learning systems — training and inference infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;off-the-clock&#34;&gt;Off the Clock&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;🎮 Games · 📖 Web novels · 🎬 Anime&lt;/p&gt;</description>
